Text: Financial SWAPs database Cc Per our telephone conversation please provide myself and Donna Lowry access to the Financial SWAPs lotus notes database As I indicated during our conversation both myself and Donna Lowry work in the RAC group and need the same access as the Credit group in particular Tanya Rohauer Other individuals within our group will need access eventually and I will send you a separate email at that time If I have any questions once Im in the database I will call you Thanks for your help Shemeika Landry

FW lotus notes link Cc Tana for following up on our discussion with Mark Taylor and Sara on Friday Mike was scheduled to come on Friday and provide me the server that your database is located on I did tell him of our efforts to try to determine the server when I came to your office He did indicate that the did not think it was a CORP vs ECT domain issue Mike will hopefully come to help us out today or this week Thanks Shemeika Original Message From Jones Tana Sent Monday June AM To Landry Shemeika S Cc Shackleton Sara Subject lotus notes link I have submitted the security requests to get the three of you access to the Other Agreements subdirectory of the Financial Agreement Database That approval usually takes about a day as soon as it comes through Ill let you know You will of course still need to solve how to get into the directory with Mike Neves Let me know when you can get in Forwarded by Tana JonesHOUECT on AM Sara Shackleton AM To Tana CT cc Subject lotus notes link Tana The following people have requested a link Donna Lowry Shemeika Landry Shelli Smith Shemeika and Shelli work with Donna in risk analytics Thanks Sara Shackleton Enron North America Corp Smith Street EB a Houston Texas phone fax
